#: src/Sum/ByUnsaturatedBounds/ByOffset/Delta9.md:1
msgid "Sum of delta 9 fatty acids"
msgstr "Сумма дельта 9 жирных кислот"

#: src/Sum/ByUnsaturatedBounds/ByOffset/Delta9.md:3
msgid "$$\\sum \\ce{UFA(\\Delta{9})}$$"
msgstr "$$\\sum \\ce{UFA(\\Delta{9})}$$"

