msgid "$$\\frac{\\ce{C{12:0}} + 4 \\times \\ce{C{14:0}} + \\ce{C{16:0}}}{\\sum \\ce{MUFA} + \\sum \\ce{PUFA(\\omega-6)} + \\sum \\ce{PUFA(\\omega-3)}} \\tag{1, 3-5}$$"
